If you can't make it to the mountains to visit any of the Buddhist monasteries in India, the Namdroling Monastery and Golden Temple in south India is well worth seeing instead. The Tibetan settlement there is apparently the second largest in India.f you can't make it to the mountains to visit any of the Buddhist monasteries in India, the Namdroling Monastery and Golden Temple in south India is well worth seeing instead. The Tibetan settlement there is apparently the second largest in India.
